<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">According to Wikipedia the original title was &quot;Napoleon the Great&quot;, the American edition being titled &quot;Napoleon: A Life&quot;. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">According to Wikipedia the original title was "Napoleon the Great", the American edition being titled "Napoleon: A Life". <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
