<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1874675-is-this-book-fine-to-read-with-only">Is this book fine to read with only rudimentary knowledge of the history Napoleon and his importance? If not, what books are better to start with?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1874675'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F20821092-napoleon">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
